Modifications made by Israel Mosquera in 2026 (per Apache-2.0 section 4(b)):
  - Translated and adapted the guidance to Spanish for the opencode runtime on
    Windows (SKILL.md, references/schemas.md).
  - Rewrote the validation/packaging scripts to remove the PyYAML dependency,
    using a custom frontmatter parser (scripts/utils.py).
  - Added scripts/init_skill.py to scaffold new opencode skills.
  - Replaced the automated Claude Code eval/benchmark harness (run_eval.py,
    run_loop.py, aggregate_benchmark.py, generate_report.py, the eval viewer and
